                       p Angel's Billabong is often included in the list of recommendations for anyone on vacation to Bali, especially when crossing to Nusa Penida Island. Indeed, even though you have to cross to Nusa Penida to visit Angel's Billabong, you certainly won't regret having to 'go to great lengths' to be able to enjoy amazing natural treats while there.
                 
