                       p Atuh beach is a beach located in the eastern area of Nusa Penida, is a very popular new tourist attraction in Nusa Penida because this beach offers natural beauty with clear water and the atmosphere of the beach surrounding the cliffs adds to the beauty of this beach. Atuh beach is perfect for swimming with a stretch of white sand to make the atmosphere more beautiful swimming. To reach the beach location or you can go down the stairs provided, you need good stamina to be able to go down the road to the beach. no wonder if this beach is very popular among domestic and foreign tourists because this beach is suitable for those who want to enjoy the atmosphere of a calm beach, not crowded and the scenery around a beautiful beach
                 
